<DATELINE>BOSTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Police are searching for a thief; they say someone
has been stealing the fancy doorknobs from doors at police
headquarters.
   It may be the same person who is defacing walls and signs in the
building with graffiti _ in some cases altering signs to change the
word ``legal'' to ``illegal.''
